				<view class='circleIcon'>
				</view>
				<text class='ruleTitle'>兑换价格</text>
			</view>
			<view class='ruleText'>
				<text>SEE = Seeking Experience & Engineering,意为探索用户体验与工程实践，由蚂蚁金服集团每年举办1-2次，包括专业分享、产品展台、Workshop等内容。</text>
			</view>
		</view>
		<view>
			<button bindtap='handleRule' class='iSee'>我知道了</button>
		</view>
	</view>
</view>
<view wx:else>
</view>
